                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, N</hi>59.) I produce a certificate of Haley's conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted Feb.</hi>, 1847,<hi rend="italic">having been before convicted, and confined six months</hi>)—he is the person.</p>
               <p>
